# Contact Us App — Environment Variables
#
# This application does not require any environment variables for basic operation.
# The /api/contact route handler logs submissions to the console.
#
# If you extend this app to send emails, add your provider credentials below:
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.example.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=your-email@example.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-smtp-password
# CONTACT_RECIPIENT=recipient@example.com
